## IsEqual type

Checks whether T1 can be exactly (mutually) assigned to T2

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type IsEqual<T1, T2> = T1 extends T2 ? (<G>() => G extends T1 ? 1 : 2) extends <G>() => G extends T2 ? 1 : 2 ? true : false : false;
```
